SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Canadian Food Inspection Agency Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) correct discrepancies between the French and English versions; (2) add clarity to regulatory provisions; (3) harmonize terms used in the regulations; (4) harmonize terms used in the regulations with those used in the enabling statute; (5) correct references to section numbering; and (6) correct grammatical errors.
